S"Take 250,000+ recipes (including all your own and recipes from friends), your grocery list and menus anywhere on your phone or tablet! With over eight million downloads, BigOven is the most complete cooking tool for getting inspired and organized in the kitchen and on-the-go. Anyone (no signup needed) can:\xe2\x80\xa2 Take recipes in the kitchen, to the store, on vacation - no cookbooks or recipe cards!\xe2\x80\xa2 Search recipes by keyword, course, ingredient, plus browse popular recipe collections\xe2\x80\xa2 Use up leftovers: enter three ingredients from your fridge or pantry to get ideas to make\xe2\x80\xa2 Read reviews, scale recipes, convert to metric, share recipes by email, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest\xe2\x80\xa2 Browse and share complete menus for special occasions and everyday mealsGet a free BigOven account (use the same one for BigOven.com, other devices) to:\xe2\x80\xa2 Make your own recipe collection portable, searchable, and scalable   - Save your Favorites and Recipes to Try Soon   - Add your own recipes by typing them on BigOven.com   - RecipeScan: Upload 3 photos of handwritten or typed paper recipes; we\xe2\x80\x99ll type for you   - View all your Facebook friends\xe2\x80\x99 public recipes    - Upload photos of any recipe, add recipe reviews\xe2\x80\xa2 Plan meals ahead   - Add recipes and notes onto a drag-and-drop menu planning calendar  - Save and re-use menus for one or more meals.   - Save time and money planning for everyday meals and special occasions\xe2\x80\xa2 Grocery shop with ease  - Get a grocery list created for you, automatically sorted by aisle  - Add recipes, full menus, days from the menu planner, and other needed items  - Bring your grocery list along to the store and check off items while shoppingGet an optional BigOven Pro membership to:\xe2\x80\xa2 Remove all ads on our apps and website. A single membership covers all devices.\xe2\x80\xa2 Add your own private notes on any recipes \xe2\x80\xa2 Manage your recipe collection with power tools  - Add unlimited recipes from cooking websites & blogs on BigOven.com or via web clipper  - RecipeScan: Upload 25 photos of handwritten or typed paper recipes; we\xe2\x80\x99ll type for you   - Create your own private custom variation of any BigOven recipe on BigOven.com\xe2\x80\xa2 Eat better with nutrition tools  - See calories, fat, sodium and more on recipes and individual ingredients  - Vegetarian, Vegan, No Red Meat, No Dairy, No Nuts, No Gluten, No Shellfish collections  - Search recipes by dietary constraint  - Exclude multiple ingredients when searchingGet BigOven's free apps for other devices too - all data syncs via the cloud for free.See our demo: http://www.bigoven.comHappy cooking!Recent changes:Bug fixes"
